Obumbro.text: Order executed before your telegram arrived

Obvagio.text: All your orders have been executed

Obvertunto.text: Have received your order. Goods will be despatched to-day

Obvigilat.text: Have received your order. Goods will be despatched to-morrow

Obvigilavi.text: Have received your order. Goods will be despatched this week

Obvigilo.text: Have received your order. Goods will be despatched next week

Obviam.text: Have received your order. Goods will be despatched in --- weeks

Obvius.text: Have you executed our last order

Obvolvunt.text: Reply by post when you will despatch our order of ---

Occallatus.text: Reply by telegram when you will despatch our order of ---

Occalleo.text: This order is in addition to previous

Occanere.text: This order is in substitution of previous

Occano.text: This order must leave you on

Occasiones.text: When is the earliest you can deliver order
